properties.Name: FastqIlluminaSequenceIdentifierPostVersion13
properties.Description:
Illumina sequence identifiers post version 1.3

Ex:
@EAS139:136:FC706VJ:2:2104:15343:197393 1:N:18:1

where:
EAS139   the unique instrument name
136         the run id
FC706VJ the flowcell id
2             flowcell lane
2104       tile number within the flowcell lane
15343     'x'-coordinate of the cluster within the tile
197393   'y'-coordinate of the cluster within the tile
1             the member of a pair, 1 or 2 (paired-end or mate-pair reads only)
Y             Y if the read is filtered, N otherwise
18           0 when none of the control bits are on, otherwise it is an even number
ATCACG index sequence

Columns.Name: ReadFilteredIndicator
Columns.Description: If Y if the read is filtered, N otherwise it is not.

Columns.Description: 0 when none of the control bits are on, otherwise it is an even number.
